{"tid":413194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到肥過我嘅人就可以加強我減肥嘅毅力","createTime":"2017-09-25T09:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T11:55:26.000Z","uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59ee0c96593b2803a8fc4b76948fe7145fddc183","tid":413194,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"減緊肥，早餐食一碗豆腐花加飯團一個<br />\n<br />\n中午唔食<br />\n<br />\n夜晚食兩碗蔬菜，放假日子獎勵自己食個生果<br />\n<br />\n禁肉，非宗教原因，只為破釜沉舟<br />\n利申：份工要體力勞動，臨收工會腳軟同頭暈<br />\n<br />\n原本今日路過小食檔差d破戒<br />\n但一見到個肥妹行左入KFC我就如夢初醒<br />\n<br />\n勸減緊肥嘅巴絲打一句，減肥係一個折磨自己，摧毀心智嘅行為<br />\n要狠，要絕，要從自己嘅痛苦中獲取快樂同成功感<br />\n<br />\n中碼衫，我來了!"},{"pid":"d49c35f1c6675ec1c34fedb2377ea347ebe53138","tid":413194,"uid":59595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"你要工作既話應該控制卡路里就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食太少影響代謝 你連肉都唔食根本唔好減 蛋白質減肥上仲重要過澱粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 肥仔"},{"pid":"bdcd8e1d72621dac4e5fc51d3cd327af3ebef128","tid":413194,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要工作既話應該控制卡路里就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食太少影響代謝 你連肉都唔食根本唔好減 蛋白質減肥上仲重要過澱粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 肥仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以你係肥仔，唔好信咩計卡路里，依賴佢只會令到意志薄弱<br />\n<br />\n捷徑必然滿佈荊棘，最珍貴嘅事物只存在地獄之中"},{"pid":"6133b0be20734a04ec5abf684779a903347fe50b","tid":413194,"uid":59595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"我只係從科學角度 比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你喜歡可以飲水減肥都得 一樣咁地獄"},{"pid":"99dda373b8795a8cf53e73512063448c78f39c0f","tid":413194,"uid":88235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:55:05.000Z","msg":"分左半個月絕食咁瘦左4kg <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95594803e5e54611a224e9973b5f60c547ff14b","tid":413194,"uid":88235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手半個月絕食咁瘦左4kg <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}